<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBa9_00099" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBa9_00099_F001">
<sentence>源蔵の手は、どうしようもなく小きざみにふるえてしま<sampling type="start" />う。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>片方の手で、片方をおさえる源蔵。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">玄白</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<verse>
<sentence type="verse">「〽人はだれでも<verseLine />いつかは、サヨナラをするものさ<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">だけど<verseLine />だけど<verseLine />こんなサヨナラはしたくない<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">こんなサヨナラだけはしたくない<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">人はなんの為に生きていくのか<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">人はなんの為に死んでいくのか」<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</verse>
</speech>
</quotation>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">●　舞台で</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<sentence>源内、玄白、そしてビワたちがスポットの中で合唱する。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<verse>
<sentence type="verse">〽赤穂浪士も人間だ、<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">義士とか、チューとか<verseLine />いわないで<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">思い出したら<verseLine />思い出したら<verseLine />そこらの花を手につんで<verseLine />芝の泉岳寺にいっとくれ<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">こんど、生まれるその時は<verseLine />オサムライさんにはなるんじゃない<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="verse">タダの人間に<verseLine />うまれておいでェ！<verseLine /></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</verse>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>一同、礼。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>上から桜吹雪がふる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>顔をあげると、場内、わずかに紅と夢蔵が二人、パチパチと拍手するのみ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>紅もなんか気の毒そう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>寺子屋の子供たちは、グウグウ眠っている。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">紅</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「さ、終ったよ、帰るからおきなさい」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">源内</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「（がっくり）…お客はゼロか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">玄白</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「ほんとだ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>なおも桜吹雪。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">源内</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「夢蔵さん、すみません…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">夢蔵</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「いやァ…やっぱり、ウソの忠臣蔵にはかないませんでしたね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">源内</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「みんなは、ホントがきらいなのかなあ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">玄白</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>「いや、そんなことはない。</sentence>
<sentence>いつか、きっとホントをほしがるようになるよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">さ、みなさんご苦労さんでした」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">一同</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「（力なく）お疲れさんでしたァ…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>と、散っていく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧の声</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>「おーい！</sentence>
<sentence>　大変だ、大変だ！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">玄白</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「もう終りですよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>上から稲葉小僧がとびおりる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「おい、まわりは、御用提灯の渦だぜ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">源内</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「え！！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「これじゃ、お客はよりつかねェよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">源内</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>「そうか！</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（やっぱり）」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>外で御用！</sentence>
<sentence>　御用！</sentence>
<sentence>　の声。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">夢蔵</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「子供を連れて皆、こっちへ来て下さい」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">玄白</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「これはもう駄目だ、逃げられないや」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">夢蔵</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「大丈夫、抜け穴は作ってあります」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「さすがあ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">夢蔵</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「どうも昔のくせが出てね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>紅、子供達、抜け穴を出て行く。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>稲葉小僧、源内、玄白残る。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>御用、御用の声と共に、くらい客席に御用提灯が何十と。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">役人</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>「ご政道批判の芝居、不とどき至極！</sentence>
<sentence>　御用である！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>みると、舞台の源内、玄白たち、黒子で顔をかくす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「さ、早くいきな、あとは本職にまかしときなって」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">源内</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「じゃ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>源内ら、玄白らと舞台裏へかけこむ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>ぴゅっととびあがると、もう天井。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>稲葉小僧、花道へドドド、とかけて、パッときまった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「さあ、さあ御用というんだから、そっちから用件をいったらどうでェ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>ピュッ、ピュッと棒やナワがとんでくるのを、かわして見得をきった。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">稲葉小僧</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「やっと、役にありつけた」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>あとは、あっちへピョイ、こっちへピョイ、役人をホンロウして、稲葉小僧、にげてゆく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>〈こんなわけで、江戸神保町の極楽座、建つには建ったんですが、記録にはのこっておりません。</sentence>
<sentence>小僧さーん、つかまらないでね！〉</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>ノボリなどが役人の土足にふみにじられて泥だらけです。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>路地を右京之介、八萬、歌いながら歩いてくる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence>楠木正成の歌。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">右京之介</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>「みん<sampling type="end" />な、分ってないんだな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（八萬に）お前だけだ、わかってくれるのは」</sentence>
</sentence>
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
